{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.playState","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><em><code>playState</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>La propiedad&nbsp; <code><strong>Animation</strong></code><strong><code>.playState</code></strong> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a> devuelve y establece un valor enumerado que describe el estado de reproducción de una animación.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>Esta propiedad es de solo lectura para las Animaciones y Transiciones en CSS.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var<em> currentPlayState</em> = <em>Animation</em>.playState;\n\n<em>Animation</em>.playState = <em>newState</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"idleinactivo\"><code>idle(inactivo)</code></dt>\n <dd><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>El tiempo actual de la animación no está resuelto y no hay tareas pendientes.</span></span></dd>\n <dt id=\"pendingpendiente\"><code>pending(pendiente)</code></dt>\n <dd><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>La animación está esperando que se complete una tarea pendiente.</span></span></dd>\n <dt id=\"runningfuncionando\"><code>running(funcionando)</code></dt>\n <dd><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>La animación se está ejecutando.</span></span></dd>\n <dt id=\"pausedpausado\"><code>paused(pausado)</code></dt>\n <dd><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>La animación se ha suspendido y la propiedad <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>Animation.currentTime</code></a> no se está actualizando.</span></span></dd>\n <dt id=\"finishedfinalizado\"><code>finished(finalizado)</code></dt>\n <dd><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>La animación ha alcanzado uno de sus límites y la propiedad <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>Animation.currentTime</code></a> no se está actualizando.</span></span></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Growing/Shrinking Alice Game</a> , los jugadores pueden tener un final con (Alicia llorando en un mar de lágrimas) <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/EPJdJx?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Alice crying into a pool of tears</a>. En el juego, por razones de rendimiento, las lágrimas solo se deben animar cuando son visibles. <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>Por lo tanto, deben detenerse tan pronto como estén animadas, de esta manera:</span></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Configurando las animaciones de lágrimas</span>\n\ntears<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">el</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    tearsFalling<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      delay<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">getRandomMsRange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// cada lágrima aleatoria</span>\n      duration<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">getRandomMsRange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// cada lágrima aleatoria</span>\n      iterations<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">Infinity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      easing<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"cubic-bezier(0.6, 0.04, 0.98, 0.335)\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'paused'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Reproduce las lágrimas cayendo cuando el final necesita mostrarlas.</span>\n\ntears<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">el</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'playing'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Reinicia la animación de las lágrimas y la detiene.</span>\n\ntears<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">el</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playState <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"paused\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currentTime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span>","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#play-state\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'playState' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Especificaciones"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.playState","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>para otros métodos y propiedades que puede usar para controlar la animación de la página web.</span></span></li>\n <li>Los métodos&nbsp; <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>Animation.play()</code></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>Animation.pause()</code></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>Animation.finish()</code></a> pueden establecer el <code>playState</code> de un&nbsp; <code>Animation</code> .</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span>","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad  Animation.playState de la Web Animations API devuelve y establece un valor enumerado que describe el estado de reproducción de una animación.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.playState","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.playState","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Animation.playState","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/playstate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/playstate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState","title":"Animation.playState"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.playState - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}